---
title: compute_cells (fulu-polynomial-commitments-sampling)
---
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB

    [*] --> q_init : start
    q_init --> q_assert : assert len(blob) == BYTES_PER_BLOB
    q_assert --> q_poly : polynomial = blob_to_polynomial(blob)
    q_poly --> q_coeff : polynomial_coeff = polynomial_eval_to_coeff(polynomial)
    q_coeff --> q_init_cells : cells = []
    q_init_cells --> q_iter : for i in range(CELLS_PER_EXT_BLOB)
    q_iter --> q_coset : coset = coset_for_cell(CellIndex(i))
    q_coset --> q_eval : ys = [evaluate_polynomialcoeff(poly_coeff, z) for z in coset]
    q_eval --> q_append : cells.append(coset_evals_to_cell(ys))
    q_append --> q_iter : next cell
    q_iter --> q_return : all cells computed
    q_return --> [*] : return cells

    note right of q_coeff
        INV: Input blob must be exactly BYTES_PER_BLOB bytes
        INV: Output contains exactly CELLS_PER_EXT_BLOB cells
        INV: Each cell represents polynomial evaluations over a distinct coset
    end note
